LCH.Clearnet Lowers Margins for LME Zinc, Molybdenum, Steel

-- B y   A g n i e s z k a   T r o s z k i e w i c z
-- 
2011-06-02T16:39:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/lch-clearnet-lowers-margins-for-lme-zinc-molybdenum-steel-1-.html
LCH.Clearnet lowered margins for
zinc, mini zinc, molybdenum and steel billet on the London Metal
Exchange, effective June 8.  Margins for zinc and mini zinc contracts will drop to $210
a metric ton from $240, the clearing house said today on its
website. Margins for molybdenum will decrease to $3,800 a ton
from $4,100, while Mediterranean steel billet margins will fall
to $40 a ton from $45,  Europe â€™s biggest clearing house said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
